{"tid":409510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[好奇一問] 大家頹嗰陣會暴食定厭食？","createTime":"2017-09-22T06:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T20:16:55.000Z","uid":124427,"like":16,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a55c3148040bef74cd9c9bf1355474af2f539d64","tid":409510,"uid":124427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:10:14.000Z","msg":"我自己之前頹係會暴飲暴食 <br />\n然後心情真係會好好多 越食越開心<br />\n仲會催眠自己食得是福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔知點解過咗一排壓力大翻心情唔好又無哂胃口<br />\n直頭見到食物都唔開胃 食多餐都好厭<br />\n<br />\n好似幾矛盾<br />\n所以都好好奇想知大家係點？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 暴食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 厭食"},{"pid":"ccc78ebffc32e6aeb7f8b4b2f206bc1d3a9cbc42","tid":409510,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:11:09.000Z","msg":"食閪屎算咩 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f75dae0260fce8161a219641d55b80ae36b1cf","tid":409510,"uid":144783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己之前頹係會暴飲暴食 <br />\n然後心情真係會好好多 越食越開心<br />\n仲會催眠自己食得是福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔知點解過咗一排壓力大翻心情唔好又無哂胃口<br />\n直頭見到食物都唔開胃 食多餐都好厭<br />\n<br />\n好似幾矛盾<br />\n所以都好好奇想知大家係點？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 暴食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 厭食</blockquote><br />\n我同你相反,我頹係會厭食,成日唔食"},{"pid":"f7ab4bc2c974b8ca6ec1c048cea1683bf9c615ff","tid":409510,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:15:21.000Z","msg":"兩款都試過"},{"pid":"4e0658bf4227396b6f59f29b8080e60aa96cb051","tid":409510,"uid":129829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:16:44.000Z","msg":"頹就厭食 <br />\n嬲就暴食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"