7d075ac0823bc61c78471db0e6a213317c23bb6b","tid":409510,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:40:32.000Z","msg":"我都想暴食<br />\n<br />\n一頹就會冇曬心機食嘢，Feel 唔到肚餓<br />\n<br />\n本身已經瘦，仲成日唔開心嘅話<br />\n<br />\n會畀人話營養不良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587fe8cb9cd2d276813e772fcc9c19ecd8239cea","tid":409510,"uid":45646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:46:18.000Z","msg":"暴食<br />\n唔飽會覺得好空虛，同埋覺得有得諗食乜好幸福，咬嗰下呑嗰下都好幸福。<br />\n<br />\n但試過幾次壓力大胃痛，食唔到嘢，嗰陣覺得人生冇意義，連食都食唔到，真係會想死。"},{"pid":"734e48900bf1ef4ff274f27c7a2c9c9c7fd8ac0b","tid":409510,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想暴食<br />\n<br />\n一頹就會冇曬心機食嘢，Feel 唔到肚餓<br />\n<br />\n本身已經瘦，仲成日唔開心嘅話<br />\n<br />\n會畀人話營養不良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係好營養不良feel既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我食好多菜 好少肉 但就係肥唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30243cdfe6be68c19bcb674f43c6c92537eaa180","tid":409510,"uid":124427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一開心就約多個FD<br />\n兩人食四人桶餐</blockquote><br />\n頹就修仙</blockquote><br />\n咁樣都幾好 但唔可以情緒起伏太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係一時食多一時食少都對個胃不大好"},{"pid":"c4ac018e0aa4051c8a0cd43ab64df483b9f4c158","tid":409510,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:50:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食閪屎算咩 ?<img src=\"